---
title: Paprika Pork Mince Pasta with bell pepper and parsley
description: Succulent pork mince is lightly spiced with paprika while a sprinkling of cheese and a dollop of creme fraiche ties the whole thing together for a simple and satisfying rigatoni recipe.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R06_W31_IE_IEXFP25671-2_Mainhigh-8fcea517.jpg
